---
title: Prawn and Tomato Risotto with Chilli and Parsley
description: Looking for a light and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Prawn, Chilli & Tomato Risotto for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prawn-and-tomato-risotto-d888c1f5-4dd42eab.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/prawn-and-tomato-risotto-5fe31262ffbca863e22bcc0a-5748859d.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Italian
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/prawn-and-tomato-risotto-5fe31262ffbca863e22bcc0a
author: Mimi Morley
time required: 35 minutes
